    <section class="learning-section">
        <h4>Project Description</h4>
        <p>
            This chat room system project has been an incredible opportunity to dive deep into web development with the ASP.NET framework. The project involved creating a fully functional chat application where users can join, send messages, and interact with each other in real-time.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="learning-section">
        <h4>Technical Skills Acquired</h4>
        <p>
            Throughout this project, I have enhanced my skills in:
            <ul>
                <li>ASP.NET Framework</li>
                <li>C# Programming Language</li>
                <li>JavaScript & jQuery</li>
                <li>SignalR for real-time communication</li>
                <li>HTML5 & CSS3 for creating responsive and visually appealing designs</li>
            </ul>
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="learning-section">
        <h4>Key Features Implemented</h4>
        <p>
            The chat room system includes several key features that showcase my understanding of modern web development:
            <ul>
                <li>Real-time messaging with live updates using SignalR</li>
                <li>Dynamic user interaction, including join and leave notifications</li>
                <li>Customizable UI with creative hover effects and responsive design</li>
                <li>Secure user handling and session management</li>
            </ul>
        </p>
    </section>

</main>

